<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Taller Sport Car — Administración Integral de Reparación Automotriz</title>
<meta content="Sport Car: más de 20 años administrando profesionalmente la reparación automotriz en El Salvador. Enderezado, pintura, mecánica, aire acondicionado, atención de aseguradoras y flotillas, con procesos digitales y trazabilidad completa." name="description"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@600;700;800&amp;family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&amp;family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;600&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  :root{
    --white:#FFFFFF;
    --offwhite:#F3F5F8;
    --ink:#0B0D10;
    --ink-soft:#2A2E35;
    --blue:#0F3D91;
    --blue-deep:#092A66;
    --blue-soft:rgba(15,61,145,0.08);
    --red:#E11E26;
    --red-soft:rgba(225,30,38,0.08);
    --line:#E4E7EC;
    --muted:#5B6470;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    background:var(--white);
    color:var(--ink);
    font-family:'Inter','Segoe UI',sans-serif;
    line-height:1.6;
    overflow-x:hidden;
  }
  h1,h2,h3,.display{ font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; letter-spacing:-0.01em; }
  .mono{ font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; letter-spacing:0.02em; }
  a{ color:inherit; text-decoration:none; }
  img{ max-width:100%; display:block; }
  .wrap{ max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 24px; }
  section{ position:relative; }

  /* ---------- NAV ---------- */
  header{ position:sticky; top:0; z-index:100; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92); backdrop-filter:blur(10px); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
  nav{ display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; padding:14px 24px; max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; }
  .logo img{ height:34px; width:auto; }
  .nav-links{ display:flex; gap:28px; align-items:center; }
  .nav-links a{ color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:14px; font-weight:600; transition:color .2s; }
  .nav-links a:hover{ color:var(--blue); }
  .nav-cta{ background:var(--red); color:#fff; padding:10px 20px; border-radius:8px; font-weight:700; font-size:13.5px; transition:transform .15s, box-shadow .15s; }
  .nav-cta:hover{ transform:translateY(-1px); box-shadow:0 8px 18px rgba(225,30,38,0.3); }
  .menu-btn{ display:none; background:none; border:none; font-size:24px; cursor:pointer; color:var(--ink); }

  /* ---------- HERO SLIDER ---------- */
  .hero{ position:relative; height:88vh; min-height:560px; overflow:hidden; background:var(--ink); }
  .hero-slide{ position:absolute; inset:0; background-size:cover; background-position:center; opacity:0; transition:opacity 1.4s ease; }
  .hero-slide.active{ opacity:1; }
  .hero-overlay{ position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(11,13,16,0.25) 0%, rgba(11,13,16,0.35) 45%, rgba(11,13,16,0.92) 100%); z-index:1; }
  .hero-content{ position:relative; z-index:2; height:100%; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:flex-end; padding:0 24px 64px; max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; color:#fff; }
  .hero-eyebrow{ color:var(--red); font-weight:700; font-size:13px; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:16px; }
  .hero h1{ font-size:clamp(30px,4.6vw,52px); font-weight:800; line-height:1.1; max-width:780px; margin-bottom:16px; }
  .hero p.lead{ font-size:17px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.82); max-width:560px; margin-bottom:30px; }
  .cta-row{ display:flex; gap:14px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .btn{ display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; padding:14px 26px; border-radius:8px; font-weight:700; font-size:14.5px; transition:transform .15s, box-shadow .15s, background .15s; }
  .btn-primary{ background:var(--red); color:#fff; }
  .btn-primary:hover{ transform:translateY(-2px); box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(225,30,38,0.35); }
  .btn-white{ background:#fff; color:var(--ink); }
  .btn-white:hover{ transform:translateY(-2px); box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
  .btn-outline{ border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5); color:#fff; }
  .btn-outline:hover{ background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .hero-dots{ position:absolute; z-index:2; bottom:20px; right:24px; display:flex; gap:8px; }
  .hero-dots span{ width:22px; height:3px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.35); border-radius:2px; cursor:pointer; transition:background .2s; }
  .hero-dots span.active{ background:var(--red); }

  /* ---------- INDICADORES ---------- */
  .indicators{ background:var(--ink); padding:34px 0; }
  .ind-row{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:20px; }
  .ind{ color:#fff; text-align:left; flex:1; min-width:150px; }
  .ind .num{ font-family:'Montserrat'; font-weight:800; font-size:26px; color:var(--red); }
  .ind .lbl{ font-size:12.5px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin-top:4px; }

  /* ---------- SECTION HEADS ---------- */
  .section-head{ max-width:680px; margin-bottom:44px; }
  .kicker{ color:var(--red); font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.1em; margin-bottom:14px; display:inline-block; }
  .section-head h2{ font-size:clamp(26px,3.6vw,38px); font-weight:800; margin-bottom:14px; line-height:1.15; }
  .section-head p{ color:var(--muted); font-size:16px; }
  .section-head.center{ margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; text-align:center; }

  section.reveal{ opacity:0; transform:translateY(26px); transition:opacity .7s ease, transform .7s ease; }
  section.reveal.in{ opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }

  /* ---------- DIFERENCIA ---------- */
  .diferencia{ padding:110px 0; }
  .dif-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:60px; align-items:center; }
  .dif-text p{ color:var(--muted); font-size:16.5px; margin-bottom:16px; }
  .dif-text p.big{ color:var(--ink); font-size:19px; font-weight:600; }
  .dif-visual{ display:flex; justify-content:center; }
  .dif-phone{ width:260px; border:10px solid var(--ink); border-radius:28px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 30px 60px rgba(11,13,16,0.18); }
  .dif-phone img{ width:100%; display:block; }

  /* ---------- PROCESOS DIGITALES ---------- */
  .procesos{ padding:100px 0; background:var(--offwhite); }
  .flow{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; gap:8px; margin-bottom:56px; position:relative; }
  .flow::before{ content:""; position:absolute; top:22px; left:5%; right:5%; height:2px; background:var(--line); z-index:0; }
  .flow-step{ position:relative; z-index:1; text-align:center; flex:1; min-width:0; }
  .flow-step .node{ width:44px; height:44px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--blue); color:#fff; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-family:'Montserrat'; font-weight:700; font-size:14px; margin:0 auto 12px; }
  .flow-step .lbl{ font-size:12.5px; font-weight:600; color:var(--ink-soft); padding:0 4px; }
  .proc-bottom{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:50px; align-items:start; }
  .nextrack-badge{ height:24px; width:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:14px; border-radius:6px; box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
  .proc-note{ background:var(--white); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:14px; padding:26px 28px; }
  .proc-note .tag{ font-family:'JetBrains Mono'; font-size:12px; color:var(--blue); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; margin-bottom:10px; display:block; }
  .proc-note p{ color:var(--muted); font-size:14.5px; }
  .check-list li{ list-style:none; display:flex; gap:12px; align-items:flex-start; padding:10px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); font-size:14.5px; color:var(--ink-soft); }
  .check-list li:first-child{ border-top:none; }
  .check-list li::before{ content:"✓"; color:var(--blue); font-weight:700; flex-shrink:0; }

  /* ---------- CAPACIDAD ---------- */
  .capacidad{ padding:100px 0; }
  .cap-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:56px; align-items:center; }
  .cap-photo{ border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden; }
  .cap-photo img{ width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; }
  .cap-list{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:18px; }
  .cap-item{ display:flex; gap:12px; align-items:flex-start; }
  .cap-item .ic{ width:36px; height:36px; border-radius:8px; background:var(--blue-soft); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0; }
  .cap-item .txt strong{ display:block; font-size:14.5px; font-weight:700; }
  .cap-item .txt span{ font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); }

  /* ---------- TECNOLOGIA ---------- */
  .tecnologia{ padding:100px 0; background:var(--ink); color:#fff; }
  .tecnologia .section-head p{ color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
  .tech-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:24px; margin-bottom:44px; }
  .tech-card{ background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius:14px; padding:28px; }
  .tech-card .ic{ width:42px; height:42px; border-radius:10px; background:rgba(225,30,38,0.16); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:18px; }
  .tech-card h3{ font-size:18px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .tech-card p{ color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size:14px; }
  .tech-proof{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:20px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius:14px; padding:18px; }
  .tech-proof img{ width:150px; height:90px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; flex-shrink:0; }
  .tech-proof p{ font-size:13.5px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }

  /* ---------- SERVICIOS ---------- */
  .servicios{ padding:100px 0; }
  .serv-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:24px; }
  .serv-card{ border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden; transition:transform .2s, box-shadow .2s; display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
  .serv-card:hover{ transform:translateY(-4px); box-shadow:0 16px 32px rgba(11,13,16,0.08); }
  .serv-photo{ height:180px; overflow:hidden; }
  .serv-photo img{ width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; }
  .serv-photo.icon-only{ display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:var(--blue-soft); }
  .serv-photo.icon-only svg{ width:52px; height:52px; }
  .serv-body{ padding:22px 22px 24px; flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
  .serv-body h3{ font-size:18px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .serv-body p.desc{ color:var(--muted); font-size:14px; margin-bottom:16px; flex:1; }
  .serv-more{ display:none; font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink-soft); border-top:1px solid var(--line); padding-top:14px; margin-top:2px; }
  .serv-more.open{ display:block; }
  .serv-more ul{ padding-left:18px; margin-top:6px; }
  .serv-more li{ margin-bottom:4px; }
  .ver-mas{ align-self:flex-start; font-size:13.5px; font-weight:700; color:var(--blue); border-bottom:1.5px solid var(--blue); padding-bottom:2px; cursor:pointer; background:none; border-left:none;border-right:none;border-top:none; font-family:inherit; }
  .placeholder-note{ font-size:11.5px; color:var(--red); margin-top:10px; font-style:italic; }

  /* ---------- MECANICA DEEP ---------- */
  .mecanica{ padding:100px 0; background:var(--offwhite); }
  .mec-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:0.9fr 1.1fr; gap:56px; align-items:center; }
  .mec-photo{ border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden; }
  .mec-photo img{ width:100%; display:block; }
  .mec-text p{ color:var(--muted); font-size:15.5px; margin-bottom:18px; }
  .tag-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:10px; }
  .tag-pill{ font-size:13px; font-weight:600; background:#fff; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:8px; padding:10px 14px; }

  /* ---------- EXPEDIENTE DIGITAL ---------- */
  .expediente{ padding:100px 0; }
  .exp-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:56px; align-items:center; }
  .devices{ position:relative; height:400px; }
  .device{ position:absolute; background:#fff; border:8px solid var(--ink); border-radius:14px; box-shadow:0 30px 60px rgba(11,13,16,0.18); overflow:hidden; }
  .device img{ width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; display:block; }
  .device.laptop{ width:380px; height:230px; left:0; top:70px; border-radius:10px; }
  .device.tablet{ width:170px; height:220px; left:290px; top:120px; border-radius:16px; }
  .device.phone{ width:110px; height:210px; left:255px; top:0; border-radius:20px; border-width:6px; }
  .exp-list li{ list-style:none; display:flex; gap:12px; padding:9px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); font-size:14.5px; }
  .exp-list li:first-child{ border-top:none; }
  .exp-list li::before{ content:"—"; color:var(--red); }
  .illus-note{ font-size:12px; color:var(--muted); font-style:italic; margin-top:14px; }

  /* ---------- CONTROL PRODUCCION ---------- */
  .control{ padding:100px 0; background:var(--ink); color:#fff; }
  .control .section-head p{ color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
  .control-shots{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.3fr 0.7fr; gap:24px; align-items:start; }
  .cshot{ border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.35); }
  .cshot img{ width:100%; display:block; }
  .cshot.phone{ max-width:280px; margin:0 auto; }
  .dash{ background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius:16px; padding:28px; }
  .dash-row{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.4fr 0.8fr 0.8fr 1fr 0.8fr; gap:12px; padding:14px 0; border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); font-size:13.5px; align-items:center; }
  .dash-row.head{ color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45); font-size:12px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.05em; border-top:none; }
  .dash-row:not(.head):first-of-type{ border-top:none; }
  .bar{ height:6px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius:4px; overflow:hidden; }
  .bar span{ display:block; height:100%; background:var(--red); }
  .status{ font-size:11.5px; font-weight:700; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:20px; display:inline-block; }
  .status.ok{ background:rgba(15,61,145,0.25); color:#8fb3f5; }
  .status.warn{ background:rgba(225,30,38,0.22); color:#ff9a9e; }

  /* ---------- EMPRESAS ---------- */
  .empresas{ padding:100px 0; }
  .emp-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:24px; }
  .emp-card{ border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:14px; padding:24px; }
  .emp-card h3{ font-size:15.5px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .emp-card p{ font-size:13.5px; color:var(--muted); }

  /* ---------- ASEGURADORAS ---------- */
  .aseguradoras{ padding:100px 0; background:var(--offwhite); }
  .aseg-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:56px; align-items:start; }
  .aseg-text p{ color:var(--muted); font-size:15.5px; margin-bottom:16px; }
  .pill-row{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; margin-top:20px; }
  .pill{ font-family:'Montserrat'; font-weight:700; font-size:13px; color:var(--blue); border:1px solid var(--line); background:#fff; border-radius:8px; padding:10px 16px; }
  .aseg-benefits li{ list-style:none; display:flex; gap:12px; padding:10px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); font-size:14.5px; }
  .aseg-benefits li:first-child{ border-top:none; }
  .aseg-benefits li::before{ content:"—"; color:var(--red); }

  /* ---------- GALERIA ---------- */
  .galeria{ padding:100px 0; }
  .gal-grid{ columns:4 220px; column-gap:14px; }
  .gal-item{ break-inside:avoid; margin-bottom:14px; position:relative; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden; }
  .gal-item img{ width:100%; display:block; transition:transform .3s ease; }
  .gal-item:hover img{ transform:scale(1.04); }
  .gal-cap{ position:absolute; left:0; right:0; bottom:0; padding:14px 12px; background:linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(11,13,16,0.85), transparent); color:#fff; font-size:12.5px; font-weight:600; opacity:0; transition:opacity .25s; }
  .gal-item:hover .gal-cap{ opacity:1; }

  /* ---------- OPINIONES ---------- */
  .opiniones{ padding:90px 0; text-align:center; }
  .op-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:24px; max-width:760px; margin:0 auto; }
  .op-card{ border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:14px; padding:30px 24px; }
  .op-card .stars{ color:var(--red); font-size:20px; letter-spacing:3px; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .op-card h3{ font-size:16px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .op-card p{ font-size:13.5px; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:16px; }
  .op-card a.btn{ padding:10px 20px; font-size:13.5px; }

  /* ---------- FAQ ---------- */
  .faq{ padding:90px 0; background:var(--offwhite); }
  .faq-item{ border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); padding:20px 0; cursor:pointer; }
  .faq-q{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; font-weight:700; font-size:16px; }
  .faq-q .plus{ font-size:20px; color:var(--blue); transition:transform .2s; }
  .faq-item.open .faq-q .plus{ transform:rotate(45deg); }
  .faq-a{ max-height:0; overflow:hidden; transition:max-height .3s ease; }
  .faq-item.open .faq-a{ max-height:200px; }
  .faq-a p{ color:var(--muted); font-size:14.5px; padding-top:12px; }

  /* ---------- CONTACTO ---------- */
  .contacto{ padding:100px 0; }
  .cont-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:50px; }
  .cont-info .info-row{ display:flex; gap:14px; padding:14px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); }
  .cont-info .info-row:first-child{ border-top:1px solid var(--line); }
  .cont-info .label{ width:110px; flex-shrink:0; color:var(--muted); font-size:13px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.04em; }
  .cont-info .val{ font-size:14.5px; font-weight:500; }
  .map-frame{ border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid var(--line); height:220px; margin-top:22px; }
  .map-frame iframe{ width:100%; height:100%; border:0; }
  .cform{ background:var(--offwhite); border-radius:16px; padding:30px; }
  .cform h3{ font-size:19px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .cform p.note{ color:var(--muted); font-size:13.5px; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .cform input, .cform textarea{
    width:100%; padding:12px 14px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:8px; font-family:inherit; font-size:14px; margin-bottom:12px; background:#fff;
  }
  .cform textarea{ resize:vertical; min-height:90px; }
  .cform button{ width:100%; background:var(--red); color:#fff; border:none; padding:14px; border-radius:8px; font-weight:700; font-size:15px; cursor:pointer; transition:transform .15s; }
  .cform button:hover{ transform:translateY(-2px); }

  .wa-float{
    position:fixed; bottom:22px; right:22px; z-index:200;
    width:58px; height:58px; border-radius:50%; background:#25D366; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    box-shadow:0 10px 26px rgba(0,0,0,0.28); transition:transform .2s;
  }
  .wa-float:hover{ transform:scale(1.08); }

  footer{ background:var(--ink); color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7); padding:60px 0 26px; }
  .foot-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:36px; margin-bottom:40px; }
  .foot-col h4{ color:#fff; font-size:14px; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .foot-col p, .foot-col a{ font-size:13.5px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); display:block; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .foot-col a:hover{ color:#fff; }
  .foot-badges{ display:flex; gap:10px; margin-top:6px; }
  .foot-badge{ font-size:11px; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18); border-radius:6px; padding:6px 10px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
  .foot-bottom{ border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top:22px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; font-size:12.5px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45); }

  @media (max-width:960px){
    .dif-grid,.proc-bottom,.cap-grid,.mec-grid,.exp-grid,.aseg-grid,.cont-grid,.control-shots{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .tech-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    .serv-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    .emp-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .op-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .foot-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    .nav-links{ display:none; }
    .menu-btn{ display:block; }
    .flow{ flex-wrap:wrap; }
    .flow::before{ display:none; }
    .flow-step{ flex:0 0 30%; margin-bottom:20px; }
    .gal-grid{ columns:2 160px; }
    .dash-row{ grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr 1fr; font-size:12px; }
    .dash-row span:nth-child(4), .dash-row span:nth-child(5){ display:none; }
  }
  @media (max-width:600px){
    .tech-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .serv-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .cap-list{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .ind-row{ justify-content:flex-start; }
    .ind{ min-width:44%; }
    .devices{ transform:scale(0.8); transform-origin:top left; }
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    *{ transition:none !important; animation:none !important; }
    html{ scroll-behavior:auto; }
  }
  /* ---------- EDIT MODE ---------- */
  body.edit-mode .edit{ outline:1px dashed transparent; border-radius:3px; }
  body.edit-mode .edit:hover{ outline:1px dashed var(--blue); cursor:text; }
  body.edit-mode .edit:focus{ outline:2px solid var(--red); background:rgba(225,30,38,0.05); }
  #editBanner{
    position:fixed; top:0; left:0; right:0; z-index:299; display:none;
    background:var(--blue); color:#fff; text-align:center; font-size:13px; font-weight:600; padding:9px;
  }
  #editUI{ position:fixed; bottom:22px; left:22px; z-index:300; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; }
  #editUI button{
    font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:13.5px; padding:12px 18px;
    border-radius:8px; border:none; cursor:pointer; box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
  }
  #editToggleBtn{ background:var(--blue); color:#fff; }
  #editSaveBtn{ background:var(--red); color:#fff; display:none; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
<nav>
<div class="logo"><img alt="Taller Sport Car" src="data:image/png;base64,"/></div>
<div class="nav-links">
<a href="#diferencia">Nosotros</a>
<a href="#servicios">Servicios</a>
<a href="#aseguradoras">Aseguradoras</a>
<a href="#galeria">Galería</a>
<a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
<a class="nav-cta" href="#contacto">Cotizar ahora</a>
</div>
<button class="menu-btn" id="menuBtn">☰</button>
</nav>
</header>
<section class="hero" id="hero">
<div class="hero-slide active" style="background-image:url('data:image/jpeg;base64,')"></div>
<div class="hero-slide" style="background-image:url('data:image/jpeg;base64,')"></div>
<div class="hero-slide" style="background-image:url('data:image/jpeg;base64,')"></div>
<div class="hero-slide" style="background-image:url('data:image/jpeg;base64,')"></div>
<div class="hero-overlay"></div>
<div class="hero-content">
<span class="hero-eyebrow edit">No somos un taller más</span>
<h1 class="edit">Tu vehículo merece un proceso profesional.</h1>
<p class="lead edit">Más de 20 años administrando reparaciones automotrices para particulares, empresas y las principales aseguradoras de El Salvador — con procesos digitales y trazabilidad completa, de principio a fin.</p>
<div class="cta-row">
<a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contacto">Solicitar cotización</a>
<a class="btn btn-outline" href="#contacto">Agendar inspección</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="hero-dots" id="heroDots"></div>
</section>
<section class="indicators">
<div class="wrap ind-row">
<div class="ind"><div class="num mono edit">20+</div><div class="lbl edit">Años de experiencia</div></div>
<div class="ind"><div class="num mono edit">100+</div><div class="lbl edit">Vehículos entregados / mes</div></div>
<div class="ind"><div class="num mono edit">12+</div><div class="lbl edit">Años con aseguradoras</div></div>
<div class="ind"><div class="num mono edit">75</div><div class="lbl edit">Capacidad instalada</div></div>
<div class="ind"><div class="num mono edit">35</div><div class="lbl edit">Simultáneos en producción</div></div>
<div class="ind"><div class="num mono edit">24/7</div><div class="lbl edit">Atención al cliente</div></div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="diferencia reveal" id="diferencia">
<div class="wrap dif-grid">
<div class="dif-text">
<span class="kicker edit">¿Por qué Sport Car?</span>
<h2 class="edit">Administramos la reparación. No solo la hacemos.</h2>
<p class="big edit">La diferencia no está únicamente en reparar un vehículo. La diferencia está en cómo administramos cada reparación.</p>
<p class="edit">Cada vehículo pasa por procesos definidos, controles de calidad y seguimiento digital que garantizan trazabilidad desde el ingreso hasta la entrega — algo que prácticamente ningún taller tradicional en El Salvador comunica.</p>
<p class="edit">Somos una empresa especializada en administrar integralmente la reparación de vehículos mediante procesos digitales, tecnología de pintura de precisión y un sistema propio de control de producción: <strong>NexTrack</strong>.</p>
</div>
<div class="dif-visual">
<div class="dif-phone">
<img alt="NexTrack — panel de control" src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="procesos reveal" id="procesos">
<div class="wrap">
<div class="section-head center" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
<span class="kicker edit">Procesos digitales</span>
<h2 class="edit">Control total del proceso de reparación</h2>
<p class="edit">Sport Car opera mediante NexTrack, nuestro sistema propio de administración — cada vehículo avanza por un flujo documentado, sin pasos sueltos ni información perdida.</p>
</div>
<div class="flow">
<div class="flow-step"><div class="node mono edit">01</div><div class="lbl edit">Recepción</div></div>
<div class="flow-step"><div class="node mono edit">02</div><div class="lbl edit">Inspección</div></div>
<div class="flow-step"><div class="node mono edit">03</div><div class="lbl edit">Presupuesto</div></div>
<div class="flow-step"><div class="node mono edit">04</div><div class="lbl edit">Autorización</div></div>
<div class="flow-step"><div class="node mono edit">05</div><div class="lbl edit">Producción</div></div>
<div class="flow-step"><div class="node mono edit">06</div><div class="lbl edit">Control de calidad</div></div>
<div class="flow-step"><div class="node mono edit">07</div><div class="lbl edit">Entrega</div></div>
</div>
<div class="proc-bottom">
<div class="proc-note">
<img alt="NexTrack" class="nextrack-badge" src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"/>
<p class="edit">Nuestro sistema propio de administración registra cada etapa del proceso: quién la realizó, cuánto tiempo tomó y en qué estado se encuentra. Muy pronto, nuestros clientes empresariales y aseguradoras podrán consultar en línea el estado y expediente digital de cada vehículo.</p>
</div>
<ul class="check-list">
<li class="edit">Cada etapa queda registrada</li>
<li class="edit">Se controla quién realizó cada proceso</li>
<li class="edit">Se registran tiempos reales</li>
<li class="edit">Se evita la pérdida de información</li>
<li class="edit">Se documenta todo el historial del vehículo</li>
<li class="edit">Seguimiento completo hasta la entrega</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="capacidad reveal" id="capacidad">
<div class="wrap cap-grid">
<div class="cap-photo">
<img alt="Instalaciones Taller Sport Car" src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"/>
</div>
<div>
<span class="kicker edit">Capacidad instalada</span>
<h2 class="edit" style="font-size:clamp(24px,3.2vw,32px); font-weight:800; margin-bottom:24px;">Infraestructura preparada para responder</h2>
<div class="cap-list">
<div class="cap-item"><div class="ic"><svg fill="none" height="18" stroke="#0F3D91" stroke-width="2" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="18"><rect height="10" rx="2" width="18" x="3" y="7"></rect><circle cx="7.5" cy="17" r="1.6"></circle><circle cx="16.5" cy="17" r="1.6"></circle></svg></div><div class="txt"><strong>75 vehículos</strong><span class="edit">Capacidad instalada total</span></div></div>
<div class="cap-item"><div class="ic"><svg fill="none" height="18" stroke="#0F3D91" stroke-width="2" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="18"><path d="M3 12h18M3 6h18M3 18h18"></path></svg></div><div class="txt"><strong>35 simultáneos</strong><span class="edit">En proceso de producción</span></div></div>
<div class="cap-item"><div class="ic"><svg fill="none" height="18" stroke="#0F3D91" stroke-width="2" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="18"><path d="M4 20V10l8-6 8 6v10"></path></svg></div><div class="txt"><strong>Cabina de pintura</strong><span class="edit">Profesional y controlada</span></div></div>
<div class="cap-item"><div class="ic"><svg fill="none" height="18" stroke="#0F3D91" stroke-width="2" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="18"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle></svg></div><div class="txt"><strong>Laboratorio tintométrico</strong><span class="edit">Tecnología europea BESA + Urkimix</span></div></div>
<div class="cap-item"><div class="ic"><svg fill="none" height="18" stroke="#0F3D91" stroke-width="2" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="18"><path d="M14.7 6.3a4 4 0 1 1-4.9 4.9L4 17v3h3l5.8-5.8a4 4 0 0 1 4.9-4.9l-2 2-1-1 2-2z"></path></svg></div><div class="txt"><strong>Área de mecánica</strong><span class="edit">Diagnóstico y reparación</span></div></div>
<div class="cap-item"><div class="ic"><svg fill="none" height="18" stroke="#0F3D91" stroke-width="2" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="18"><path d="M3 12h4l2-5h6l2 5h4M5 12v5h14v-5"></path></svg></div><div class="txt"><strong>Área de enderezado</strong><span class="edit">Reparación estructural</span></div></div>
<div class="cap-item"><div class="ic"><svg fill="none" height="18" stroke="#0F3D91" stroke-width="2" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="18"><path d="M12 2l2.5 7h7.5l-6 4.5 2.5 7-6-4.5-6 4.5 2.5-7-6-4.5h7.5z"></path></svg></div><div class="txt"><strong>Preparación, pulido y acabados</strong><span class="edit">Terminación de alta calidad</span></div></div>
<div class="cap-item"><div class="ic"><svg fill="none" height="18" stroke="#0F3D91" stroke-width="2" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="18"><path d="M4 4h16v16H4z"></path><path d="M4 9h16"></path></svg></div><div class="txt"><strong>Recepción especializada</strong><span class="edit">Diagnóstico inicial documentado</span></div></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="tecnologia reveal" id="tecnologia">
<div class="wrap">
<div class="section-head">
<span class="kicker edit">Tecnología</span>
<h2 class="edit">Tecnología que garantiza precisión</h2>
<p class="edit">En 2025 incorporamos tecnología europea de pintura de alta precisión, la misma utilizada en talleres de alto nivel en Europa.</p>
</div>
<div class="tech-grid">
<div class="tech-card">
<div class="ic"><svg fill="none" height="20" stroke="#E11E26" stroke-width="1.8" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="20"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"></circle><path d="M12 3a9 9 0 0 1 0 18"></path></svg></div>
<h3 class="edit">Sistema BESA</h3>
<p class="edit">Espectrofotometría digital para obtener exactamente el color original del vehículo.</p>
</div>
<div class="tech-card">
<div class="ic"><svg fill="none" height="20" stroke="#E11E26" stroke-width="1.8" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="20"><path d="M12 2l2.5 7h7.5l-6 4.5 2.5 7-6-4.5-6 4.5 2.5-7-6-4.5h7.5z"></path></svg></div>
<h3 class="edit">Urkimix Pro</h3>
<p class="edit">Sistema europeo de mezcla de pintura para acabados uniformes y duraderos.</p>
</div>
<div class="tech-card">
<div class="ic"><svg fill="none" height="20" stroke="#E11E26" stroke-width="1.8" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="20"><rect height="12" rx="1.5" width="18" x="3" y="4"></rect><path d="M8 20h8M12 16v4"></path></svg></div>
<h3 class="edit">Equipos de diagnóstico</h3>
<p class="edit">Equipos computarizados para diagnóstico mecánico y afinación de motor.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="tech-proof">
<img alt="Tecnología BESA y Urkimix en Sport Car" src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"/>
<p class="edit">Tecnología real en nuestras instalaciones: rótulo de acabados profesionales con sistema Urkimix + BESA, visible en el área de recepción del taller.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="servicios reveal" id="servicios">
<div class="wrap">
<div class="section-head">
<span class="kicker edit">Servicios</span>
<h2 class="edit">Seis líneas de trabajo, un mismo estándar</h2>
<p class="edit">Cada servicio con su propio proceso, documentado de principio a fin.</p>
</div>
<div class="serv-grid">
<div class="serv-card">
<div class="serv-photo"><img alt="Enderezado y Pintura" src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"/></div>
<div class="serv-body">
<h3 class="edit">Enderezado y Pintura</h3>
<p class="desc edit">Reparación estructural y estética con tecnología europea de color.</p>
<button class="ver-mas" data-target="m1">Ver más</button>
<div class="serv-more" id="m1">
<ul>
